; Trackside version.dll proxy — static export forwarders.
;
; Every version.dll API is forwarded, at the LOADER level, to the genuine
; version.dll shipped alongside us under the name `trackside_version.dll`
; (the deploy step copies C:\Windows\System32\version.dll to that name). The
; loader resolves these without ever running our code, which is the whole point:
; UnityPlayer.dll calls these functions extremely early (under the loader lock),
; and running our own Rust on that path is what faulted GameAssembly.dll on boot.
;
; NOTE: the right-hand side `module.Export` (a name with a dot) makes the linker
; emit a true forwarder, not a local alias. The module name has no extension —
; the loader appends `.dll` and resolves it via the normal search order (app dir
; first), so `trackside_version` → game-folder `trackside_version.dll`.
;
; This matches Night's original proxy export set exactly (17 version funcs — note
; NO GetFileVersionInfoByHandle, which UnityPlayer doesn't import and which
; link.exe won't accept as a forwarder here anyway). UnityMain / UnityMain2 are
; NOT here: they're exported as tiny runtime-forwarders in lib.rs instead (the
; .def-forwarder form to UnityPlayer fails to link, and they're not on the early
; version-API path, so a runtime forward is safe).

; Standalone chain: forward to trackside_version.dll (a renamed copy of the
; genuine System32 version.dll). For the with-Hachimi variant the user simply
; makes trackside_version.dll BE Hachimi's proxy (+hachimi/) — same proxy binary.
EXPORTS
    GetFileVersionInfoA       = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoA
    GetFileVersionInfoExA     = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoExA
    GetFileVersionInfoExW     = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoExW
    GetFileVersionInfoSizeA   = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoSizeA
    GetFileVersionInfoSizeExA = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoSizeExA
    GetFileVersionInfoSizeExW = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoSizeExW
    GetFileVersionInfoSizeW   = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoSizeW
    GetFileVersionInfoW       = trackside_version.GetFileVersionInfoW
    VerFindFileA              = trackside_version.VerFindFileA
    VerFindFileW              = trackside_version.VerFindFileW
    VerInstallFileA           = trackside_version.VerInstallFileA
    VerInstallFileW           = trackside_version.VerInstallFileW
    VerLanguageNameA          = trackside_version.VerLanguageNameA
    VerLanguageNameW          = trackside_version.VerLanguageNameW
    VerQueryValueA            = trackside_version.VerQueryValueA
    VerQueryValueW            = trackside_version.VerQueryValueW
    ; Local exports (our own Rust fns in lib.rs). A .def EXPORTS section is the
    ; authoritative export list, so these must be named here or they won't be
    ; exported at all.
    UnityMain
    UnityMain2
